SUMMARY:Erica Ambrin and The Eclectic Soul Project at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Fronted by powerhouse vocalist Erica Ambrin\, this Sonoma County–based collective brings together a rotating lineup of seasoned local musicians\, each adding their own flavor to a rich\, genre-blending sound. Rooted in soul but stretching effortlessly into funk\, jazz\, rock\, and blues\, The Eclectic Soul Project lives up to its name with dynamic arrangements and improvisational energy. \nErica’s commanding stage presence and deeply expressive vocals are the heart of the group — channeling classic soul influences while keeping things fresh\, modern\, and unmistakably local. Together\, they’ve become known around the North Bay for performances that are both musically tight and joyfully unpredictable. \nCome catch a set that’s equal parts soul revival and creative exploration.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/erica-ambrin-and-the-eclectic-soul-project-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.5205;-122.979
