UID:10018175-1774641600-1774641600@golocal.coop
SUMMARY:Marshall House Project at The Vintage Space
DESCRIPTION:MHP brings Jimi Hendrix to life on March 27 at Vintage Space with soaring guitar\, raw psychedelia\, and a night built for true Hendrix fans.\nMarshall House Project returns to Vintage Space for a special night dedicated to the music of Jimi Hendrix. Known for their fearless blend of soul\, funk\, and psychedelia\, MHP taps straight into the electricity and raw imagination that defined Hendrix. This tribute isn’t about imitation. It’s about capturing the spirit\, the edge\, and the explosive creativity that made Hendrix a singular force. \nLed by guitarist and songwriter Sam Hamby\, MHP has built a reputation for high-energy performances that bend genres and light up a room. The band’s chemistry gives them the freedom to stretch songs\, dive into improvisation\, and bring each moment alive in a way that feels immediate and unpredictable. That makes them the perfect conduit for a Hendrix-centric night. \nExpect iconic riffs\, extended solos\, swirling psychedelic passages\, and the fiery intensity that Hendrix delivered onstage. MHP approaches this material with respect and abandon\, pushing into new territory while honoring one of rock’s greatest innovators. It’s a celebration of sound\, distortion\, freedom\, and the kind of musical risk-taking that keeps audiences on their feet. \nIf you love Hendrix\, bold guitar work\, and a night that rides the line between homage and full creative expression\, this show is built for you.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/marshall-house-project-at-the-vintage-space-2/
LOCATION:Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort\, 2777 Fourth St.\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.45182;-122.68916
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort 2777 Fourth St. Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=2777 Fourth St.:geo:-122.68916,38.45182
END:VEVENT
