SUMMARY:Tainted Love at The Mystic Theatre
DESCRIPTION:The Best of the 80s Live! \nFor 2 decades\, TAINTED LOVE has been thrilling audiences nationwide with its high-energy\, over-the-top renditions of pop music from the treasure trove known as the 1980s. Their show delivers something for every music fan: pulsing dance beats\, fist-pumping rock anthems\, and guilty-pleasure sing-alongs\, all performed with the highest level of musicianship and state-of-the-art sound and lighting.
