SUMMARY:Climate Ready Cotati Fair 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join the City of Cotati for the second annual Climate Ready Cotati Fair on March 28\, 2026 from 10-2 at the Cotati SMART Depot (970 E Cotati Avenue\, Cotati\, CA 94931). The Fair is FREE and will feature 40 local agencies and organizations sharing resources\, information\, and ideas to help you live a more sustainable lifestyle and have a positive impact on the environment. Cotati’s own Sal’s Pizza and Dogs A La Carte will offer great food for sale\, featuring reusable dishes provided by Sparkl Reusables to reduce disposables waste. Prize giveaways\, kids’ activities\, an e-waste dropoff\, small appliance repair\, and much more will be available at this awesome event. Join us for activities to help you reduce\, reuse\, and recycle . . . and have fun! \nVisit the Climate Ready Cotati Fair webpage for more information: https://bit.ly/CRCFair2026
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/climate-ready-cotati-fair-2026/
LOCATION:Cotati SMART Depot\, 970 E Cotati Ave\, Cotati\, CA\, 94931\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids and Family,Other
END:VEVENT
