SUMMARY:Evening in Seville - Rotary Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:Join the Windsor Rotary Community Foundation for an unforgettable evening dedicated to strengthening our community and uplifting the next generation. On Saturday\, March 28\, Huerta Gym transforms into a vibrant celebration filled with rich flavors\, dynamic entertainment\, and a shared commitment to Empowering Windsor Youth. \nGuests will enjoy a delicious spread of tapas\, paella\, wine\, and beer\, creating the perfect setting for connection and celebration. Special guest Flamenco dancers will ignite the room with the artistry and passion of Spain\, setting the tone for an evening steeped in culture and community spirit. \nAt the heart of the night is our Silent & Live Auction\, featuring unique items\, experiences\, and local treasures—all raising essential funds for youth programs that shape Windsor’s future. \nTickets Include:\n* Tapas & Paella\n* Wine & Beer\n* Live Spanish Music\n* Flamenco Performance\n* Silent Auction\n* Live Auction \nHELP FUND THESE PROGRAMS & MORE\nWindsor Unified School District\n* Windsor Middle School AVID Program\n* AAC Communication Devices– Special Education\n* Windsor Middle School Farm to Table Program\n* Windsor Middle School Student Theatre Program\n* 5th Grade Science Camp at Nature Bridge Golden Gate \nCommunity & Youth Development Partners\n* Circuit Riders– Ecological Restoration & Workforce Training Center\n* Chief Doug Williams Gazebo– Mark West Area Community Park\n* Pacific Coast Air Museum– Student STEM Enrichment Program\n…and many more programs that inspire\, empower\, and open doors for Windsor’s youth. \nWHY YOUR SUPPORT MATTERS\nWith youth services facing increasing challenges and budget cuts\, Rotary remains steadfast in its mission to protect and expand opportunities for young people in our community. Your support—whether through sponsorship\, auction donations\, or attending the event—directly fuels these programs and keeps them thriving. \nTogether\, we can make a meaningful impact. Together\, we can raise up our youth. Together\, we can build a stronger\, brighter future for Windsor.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/evening-in-seville-rotary-fundraiser/
LOCATION:Huerta Gymnasium\, 9291 Old Redwood Highway\, Windsor\, CA
CATEGORIES:Festival
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Rotary-evening-in-seville-s.jpg
GEO:38.5495285;-122.81540991750605
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Huerta Gymnasium 9291 Old Redwood Highway Windsor CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=9291 Old Redwood Highway:geo:-122.81540991750605,38.5495285
END:VEVENT
